0) 인터페이스 주소 설정

(r4) - f0/1 - (r1) - f0/0 - (r2) - f0/1 - (r3) - f0/0 - (r5)
pe: r1, r3
p: r2
ce: r4, r5

r1
conf t
int lo0
ip add 1.1.1.1 255.255.255.255
int f0/0
no sh
ip add 1.1.12.1 255.255.255.0
int f0/1
no sh
ip add 1.1.14.1 255.255.255.0
---
r2
conf t
int lo0
ip add 2.2.2.2 255.255.255.255
int f0/0
no sh
ip add 1.1.12.2 255.255.255.0
int f0/1
no sh
ip add 1.1.23.2 255.255.255.0
---
r3
conf t
int lo0
ip add 3.3.3.3 255.255.255.255
int f0/1
no sh
ip add 1.1.23.3 255.255.255.0
int f0/0
no sh
ip add 1.1.35.3 255.255.255.0
---
r4
conf t
int lo0
ip add 4.4.4.4 255.255.255.255
int f0/1
no sh
ip add 1.1.14.4 255.255.255.0
---
r5
conf t
int lo0
ip add 5.5.5.5 255.255.255.255
int f0/0
no sh
ip add 1.1.35.5 255.255.255.0

1) IGP 구성
r1
router os 1
net 1.1.1.1 0.0.0.0 a 0
net 1.1.12.1 0.0.0.0 a 0
r2
router os 1
net 2.2.2.2 0.0.0.0 a 0
net 1.1.12.2 0.0.0.0 a 0
net 1.1.23.2 0.0.0.0 a 0
r3
router os 1
net 3.3.3.3 0.0.0.0 a 0
net 1.1.23.3 0.0.0.0 a 0

2) LDP 구성
r1
mpls lab pro ldp
mpls ldp router-id lo0
int f0/0
mpls ip
r2
mpls lab pro ldp
mpls ldp router-id lo0
int f0/0
mpls ip
int f0/1
mpls ip
r3
mpls lab pro ldp

mpls ldp router-id lo0
int f0/1
mpls ip

3) MBGP
r1
router b 10
b router-id 1.1.1.1
nei 3.3.3.3 remot 10
nei 3.3.3.3 up lo0
add vpnv4
nei 3.3.3.3 act
nei 3.3.3.3 send-com ex
r3
router b 10
b router-id 3.3.3.3
nei 1.1.1.1 remot 10
nei 1.1.1.1 up lo0
add vpnv4
nei 1.1.1.1 act
nei 1.1.1.1 send-com ex

4) vrf 
r1
ip vrf BLUE
    rd 10:100
    route-t bo 10:100
int f0/1
    ip vrf for BLUE
    ip add 1.1.14.1 255.255.255.0
r3
ip vrf BLUE
   rd 10:100
   route-t bo 10:100
int f0/0
    ip vrf for BLUE
    ip add 1.1.35.3 255.255.255.0

5) PE-CE Routing
r1
router os 10 vrf BLUE
net 1.1.14.1 0.0.0.0 a 0
redi bgp 10 sub
router b 10
add ipv4 vrf BLUE
redi os 10 mat int ex 1 ex 2
r3
router os 10 vrf BLUE
net 1.1.35.3 0.0.0.0 a 0
redi bgp 10 sub

router b 10
add ipv4 vrf BLUE
redi os 10 mat int ex 1 ex 2

r4
router os 1
net 4.4.4.4 0.0.0.0 a 0
net 1.1.14.4 0.0.0.0 a 0
r5
router os 1
net 5.5.5.5 0.0.0.0 a 0
net 1.1.35.5 0.0.0.0 a 0
